704542f-a.title: Brooklyn: Fulton Street - Gates Avenue
704542f-a.text:
Fulton Street (right), at the intersection of 7ates Avenue, viewing east. On Fulton Street is the B. M. T. "g1' and its Vanderbilt Avenue station.
June 15, 1940
P. L. Sperr
